This is a port of inxi script to ghostbsd.
inxi script is a reporting tool for console and irc.
 Inxi script is a tool to get and report various settings from your's
 computer like hardware configuration network configuration sound
 configuration Xorg configuration system configuration etc.
 Inxi output can be to console or in an irc channel.
 It's very usefull to investigate problems and report users computer
 configuration.
:
WWW: http://www.ghostbsd.org/
